This file contains notes regarding the use of mysql in the book projects:

Mysql on windows:

=== To guarantee installation of the mysql service on windows:

1. Go to control panel and bring up the user account control section by searching
for "User Account Control" in the upper right search box, then turn off
security notifications as follows in the section entitled:

Choose when to be notified about changes to your computer

Drag the bar from "Always Notify" to "Never Notify"

2. Reboot your computer.

3. Then run the following command:

$MYSQL_HOME/bin/mysqld --install

4. reboot your computer.

=== To set the mysql root password, execute the instructions on the following
page:

http://dev.mysql.com/doc/refman/5.0/en/resetting-permissions.html

